2020年8月7日，[[美國財政部|美國財政部]]宣佈，制裁包括盧偉聰在內的11名“侵犯[[香港人權|香港人權]]”的内地与香港官員<ref name="thestandnews-2020-08-08">{{cite news |title=美財政部列制裁 11 中港官員原因：林鄭配合北京打壓港人自由、鄧炳強領警攻理大 |url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E5%88%97%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-11-%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E9%A0%98%E8%AD%A6%E6%94%BB%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7/ |accessdate=2020-08-12 |work=立場新聞 |date=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809034616/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E5%88%97%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-11-%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E9%A0%98%E8%AD%A6%E6%94%BB%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，公開其個人資料<ref>[https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53700444 美國宣佈制裁11名中港官員，林鄭月娥首當其衝] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53700444 |date=20200808130218 }}，2020年8月7日，BBC</ref>，並列入《[[特別指定國民和被封鎖人員|特別指定國民和被封鎖人員]]》，被美國執行制裁者除了美國資產被凍結，不能使用美國銀行及公司提供的服務，其在香港及海外的銀行服務亦極可能被取消<ref>{{cite news |author1=羅冠聰 |title=深度剖析美國制裁的後果、影響以及中共反制可能 |url=https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%8C%E6%9E%9C-%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD/ |publisher=立場新聞 |date=2020-08-08 |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2020-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815130040/https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%8C%E6%9E%9C-%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。盧偉聰在出任警務處處長期間被指[[對於反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動中香港警隊的批評|縱容警暴]]，即使其已於2019年11月離任，但未能與其在任內警隊犯下的多起侵害人權事件切割<ref name="rfa-2020-08-07">{{cite news |title=美財政部制裁林鄭月娥等11人　退休前警務處處長盧偉聰難逃法網 |url=https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/US-breakingnews-08072020121123.html |accessdate=2020-08-12 |work=RFA |date=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325230727/https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/US-breakingnews-08072020121123.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Hong Kong-related Designations; Central African Republic Designation |url=https://www.treasury.gov/resource-center/sanctions/OFAC-Enforcement/Pages/20200807.aspx |publisher=U.S. DEPARTMENT OF THE TREASURY |date=2020-08-07 |accessdate=2020-08-12 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200808063947/https://www.treasury.gov/resource-center/sanctions/OFAC-Enforcement/Pages/20200807.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="sm1087">{{cite news |title=Treasury Sanctions Militia Leader in Central African Republic for Human Rights Abuse |url=https://home.treasury.gov/news/press-releases/sm1087 |publisher=U.S. DEPARTMENT OF THE TREASURY |date=2020-08-07 |accessdate=2020-08-12 |archive-date=2020-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822092851/https://home.treasury.gov/news/press-releases/sm1087 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。盧偉聰被制裁後，回應指美國政府蠻不講理、制裁並不公平，他表示極度遺憾和憤慨<ref>{{cite news |title= 盧偉聰回應被制裁稱極遺憾　指美國政府蠻不講理 |url= https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542616-20200808.htm |publisher= 香港電台 |date= 2020-08-08 |accessdate= 2020-08-09 |archive-date= 2020-11-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201123125343/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542616-20200808.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

